author: danj
msg: New sample project that illustrates usage of WSN producer (pubsub). This resource type also includes many
of the MUWS capabilities, which adds the manageability properties to the WSRP document. The custom capability
in the sample publishes a simple message every 7 seconds; if the wsn-consumer sample is subscribed to this
producer, you should see it print a message every 7 seconds or so.
